OL,3,CMinister 'sorry' to former soldier
OL,4,Cturned away from polling station over
OL,5,CID
OL,7,F"I spent 27 years in the Army and
OL,8,Ftoday I was going to vote in my local
OL,9,Felections."
OL,11,FVoters have been required to show
OL,12,Fphoto ID at the ballot box following
OL,13,Freforms introduced by the government
OL,14,Fin May last year.
OL,16,FHowever, the new veteran ID card,
OL,17,Fwhich was introduced earlier this
OL,18,Fyear, is not among those accepted.
