OL,7,FMr Diver went on to say he will be
OL,8,F"fighting" for his ID to be considered
OL,9,Fas "more formal".
OL,11,FJohnny Mercer, the Conservative MP for
OL,12,FPlymouth Moor View, said he was sorry
OL,13,Ffor Mr Diver's experience and says he
OL,14,Fwill do "all he can" to make the
OL,15,FVeteran Card an acceptable form of ID
OL,16,Ffor future elections.
