OL,3,CMinister 'sorry' to former soldier
OL,4,Cturned away from polling station over
OL,5,CID
OL,7,FIn a statement, Mr Mercer, who is also
OL,8,Fa former soldier, said: "The
OL,9,Flegislation on acceptable forms of ID
OL,10,Fcame out before the veterans ID cards
OL,11,Fstarted coming out in January this
OL,12,Fyear. I will do all I can to change it
OL,13,Fbefore the next one.
OL,15,F"We're delivering on our commitment to
OL,16,Froll out Veteran Cards, with tens of
OL,17,Fthousands of cards issued since
OL,18,Flaunching the online portal earlier
OL,19,Fthis year.
