OL,5,CID
OL,7,F"While the Veteran Card cannot be used
OL,8,Fat polling stations today, I want to
OL,9,Freassure you that we are already
OL,10,Fconsulting on accepting their use in
OL,11,Ffuture elections.
OL,13,F"It's important to me that veterans
OL,14,Fare able to make the most of their
OL,15,Fcard and I will have more to say about
OL,16,Fthis in due course."
